OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784053120
OL,3,CDrug dealer who shot burglar dead
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FA drug dealer who armed himself with a
OL,7,Fsawn-off shotgun before murdering a
OL,8,Fburglar has been jailed for at least
OL,9,F27 years.
OL,11,FAdrian Frost, 61, fired at 26-year-old
OL,12,FConnor Batty from the top of a
OL,13,Fstaircase after a gang of three broke
OL,14,Finto his home in Barnsley Road,
OL,15,FHemsworth, West Yorkshire.
OL,17,FThe gang had targeted his property
OL,18,Farmed with an imitation handgun, a
OL,19,Fpickaxe handle and garden shears,
OL,20,Fintent on stealing cannabis and
OL,21,Fvaluables on 11 September last year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
