FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784053120
OL,3,CDrug dealer who shot burglar dead
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FFrost mocked Batty as he lay dying and
OL,7,Fsent his brother a message saying he
OL,8,Fhad carried out the killing.
OL,10,FBatty's accomplices initially tried to
OL,11,Fdrag him from the scene before fleeing.
OL,13,FWhen officers searched the address,
OL,14,Fthey found the shotgun along with an
OL,15,Farray of other weapons, including an
OL,16,Fillegal high-powered air rifle, a
OL,17,FSamurai sword, machetes, knuckle
OL,18,Fdusters and incapacitant spray.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
