FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784053120
OL,3,CDrug dealer who shot burglar dead
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FCCTV footage showed Frost in his
OL,7,Fdining room immediately after the
OL,8,Fshooting, holding the murder weapon
OL,9,Fand with shotgun cartridges around his
OL,10,Fneck and in his mouth.
OL,12,FAfter his arrest Frost claimed he had
OL,13,Fslipped and fired the shotgun
OL,14,Faccidentally, but at court claimed he
OL,15,Fhad been terrified and acted in self-
OL,16,Fdefence.
OL,18,FHe was convicted last week after a
OL,19,Ftrial.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
