FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784053120
OL,3,CDrug dealer who shot burglar dead
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FHe had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fpossession of the shotgun, production
OL,8,Fof cannabis, supplying cannabis,
OL,9,Fpossession of incapacitant spray and
OL,10,Fabstraction of electricity.
OL,12,FOn Monday Frost was sentenced to life
OL,13,Fin prison with a minimum term of 27
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FBatty's accomplices were sentenced in
OL,17,FMay for their involvement in the
OL,18,Fincident.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
